{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "ada3442f-62e9-4827-b9ba-1182c2396d96", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ada3442f-62e9-4827-b9ba-1182c2396d96@1.pkg/1772597709812/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597710087", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ada3442f-62e9-4827-b9ba-1182c2396d96@1.pkg/1772597709812/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597710087"}, "identifier": "ada3442f-62e9-4827-b9ba-1182c2396d96", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查 &ldquo;拥有积极的人生态度&rdquo; 的知识点。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>袁隆平院士在困难中保持乐观坚韧、积极进取的人生态度，与 &ldquo;千磨万击还坚劲，任尔东西南北风&rdquo; 所体现的不畏艰难、顽强执着的态度一致，故 B 正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A 体现的是爱国情怀和生死观，与积极人生态度的核心（面对困难的乐观坚韧）不符；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C 表达的是爱情观，与题意无关；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D 强调的是认识事物需跳出局部视角，属于认识论范畴，与人生态度无关；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>答案选 B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">袁隆平院士投身杂交水稻研究后，曾面对实验田被毁、数据丢失等重重挫折，但他从未气馁，还常鼓励团队：&ldquo;失败了就再来，只要坚持下去，总会成功的。&rdquo; 正是这种积极态度，让他带领团队攻克了杂交水稻培育的诸多难题。下列诗句所体现的人生态度与袁隆平院士一致的是（ ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）袁隆平院士投身杂交水稻研究后，曾面对实验田被毁、数据丢失等重重挫折，但他从未气馁，还常鼓励团队：“失败了就再来，只要坚持下去，总会成功的。” 正是这种积极态度，让他带领团队攻克了杂交水稻培育的诸多难题。下列诗句所体现的人生态度与袁隆平院士一致的是（ ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ada3442f-62e9-4827-b9ba-1182c2396d96@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984698005", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">人生自古谁无死，留取丹心照汗青</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">千磨万击还坚劲，任尔东西南北风</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">两情若是久长时，又岂在朝朝暮暮</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">不识庐山真面目，只缘身在此山中</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">袁隆平院士投身杂交水稻研究后，曾面对实验田被毁、数据丢失等重重挫折，但他从未气馁，还常鼓